a date.\n    * Depending on the Allocation start convention, the Reserve allocation start date is different.  \n9. Click Filter.\n10. In the Criteria field, type a value.\n11. Click OK.\n12. Click OK.\n13. Click Post.\n\n","nodes":[{"pos":[5,618],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"# required metadata \n \ntitle: Propose special depreciation (Japan)\ndescription: In Japan, a special depreciation is permitted under certain conditions. \nauthor: ShylaThompson\nmanager: AnnBe \nms.date: 02/26/2016\nms.topic: business-process \nms.prod:  \nms.service: dynamics-ax-applications \nms.technology:  \n \n# optional metadata \n \n# ms.search.form:   \naudience: Application User \n# ms.devlang:  \nms.reviewer: shylaw\nms.search.scope: Operations \n# ms.tgt_pltfrm:  \n# ms.custom:  \nms.search.region: Japan\n# ms.search.industry: \nms.author: shylaw\nms.search.validFrom: 2016-06-30 \nms.dyn365.ops.version: Version 7.0.0 ","nodes":[{"content":"Propose special depreciation (Japan)","nodes":[{"pos":[0,36],"content":"Propose special depreciation (Japan)","nodes":[{"content":"Propose special depreciation (Japan)","pos":[0,36]}]}],"path":["title"],"extradata":"MT"},{"content":"In Japan, a special depreciation is permitted under certain conditions.","nodes":[{"pos":[0,71],"content":"In Japan, a special depreciation is permitted under certain conditions.","nodes":[{"content":"In Japan, a special depreciation is permitted under certain conditions.","pos":[0,71]}]}],"path":["description"],"extradata":"MT"}],"header":"# required metadata \n","yml":true},{"pos":[625,661],"content":"Propose special depreciation (Japan)","linkify":"Propose special depreciation (Japan)","nodes":[{"content":"Propose special depreciation (Japan)","pos":[0,36]}]},{"content":"In Japan, a special depreciation is permitted under certain conditions.","pos":[731,802]},{"content":"For Reserve method, this is a two step task: post reserve, and then post reserve allocation.","pos":[803,895]},{"content":"For Di